<div class="fixed inset-0 z-[9999] pointer-events-auto" data-controller="diary-modal">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40 z-0" data-action="click->diary-modal#close"></div>

  <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center p-4 z-10">
    <div class="w-full max-w-[420px] rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-xl p-5 relative"
         data-action="click->diary-modal#stop">

      <div class="text-base font-bold">
        今日のもふもふ記録、見てみる？
      </div>

      <div class="mt-2 text-sm opacity-80 leading-relaxed">
        ※日記は1日に1回だけ作られるよ。<br>
        作ったあとは、何度でも見られるよ。
      </div>

      <div class="mt-4 flex gap-2 justify-end">
        <button type="button"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center
                       rounded-xl bg-[#bfbcbc] text-white px-4 py-2
                       hover:bg-[#a7a3a3] cursor-pointer"
                data-action="click->diary-modal#close">
          やめておく
        </button>

        <!-- link_to + turbo_method でpostのrouting errorになったので、button_toに変えました-->
        <%= button_to "見る！",
              create_today_mofu_diaries_path(format: :turbo_stream),
              method: :post,
              form: { data: { turbo_frame: "diary_modal" } },
              class: "inline-flex items-center justify-center
                      rounded-xl bg-[#ffb92f] text-white px-4 py-2
                      hover:bg-[#ffa409] cursor-pointer" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>